      • replyTo

        public ImmutableACLMessage.Builder<T> replyTo(T sender)
        create a new ACLMessage that is a reply to this message. In particular, it sets the following parameters of the new message: receivers, language, ontology, protocol, conversation-id, in-reply-to, reply-with. The programmer needs to set the communicative-act and the StringContent. Of course, if he wishes to do that, he can reset any of the fields.
        Parameters:
        sender - the sender
        Returns:
        the ACLMessage to send as a reply
